Package co.cask.cdap.api.security

This package contains interfaces and classes for CDAP security.

          Description

Class Summary
ACL Represents an entry in the Access Control List.
EntityId Identifies an entity.
Principal Represents an object that may be authorized to access various entities.
Principals Utility functions for Principals.
 

Enum Summary
EntityType Represents an entity.
PermissionType Represents groups of operations that is categorized under a permission type.
PrincipalType Represents a type of principal.
